movies.title: Club Sandwich
movies.summary: Hector and his young mother Paloma go on vacation. Out of season their hotel is deserted. They spend their days sitting on the edge of the swimming pool. Then attractive Jazmin arrives and we see how Paloma loses her son to a summer fling.

movies.title: Mayday Life
movies.summary: What is it like when a film has more than 4,150,000 actors? Mayday, the band, play the Fifth Squad of five unique superheroes. However, after the street fight, they go back to their ordinary lives and stop saving the earth. How could the captain persuade them to continue the training? What will happen to the Fifth Squad when the 122 live concerts finish?

movies.title: 1 Night
movies.summary: Bea, a worrisome teenager, reconnects with her introverted childhood friend, Andy. The two overcome their differences in social status one night after their high school prom. Thirty-something Elizabeth must decide whether to salvage her relationship with Drew after much personal disappointment. Past and present collide as two couples explore love over the course of one night at a hotel.

movies.title: Aladdin
movies.summary: Aladdin is a poor street urchin who spends his time stealing food from the marketplace in the city of Agrabah. His adventures begin when he meets a young girl who happens to be Princess Jasmine, who is forced to be married by her wacky yet estranged father. Aladdin's luck suddenly changes when he retrieves a magical lamp from the Cave of Wonders. What he unwittingly gets is a fun-loving genie who only wishes to have his freedom. Little do they know is that the Sultan's sinister advisor Jafar has his own plans for both Aladdin and the lamp.
